reviewText: This a very good product, great picture and sound quality. Tony Vega delivers a superb perfomance with a totally enganged crowd.
The sound and video quality is excellent.  Never thought we'd enjoy this DVD as much as we have; one of our favorites.  I consider it a "must buy" if you are a Tony Vega fan.

Now en sonido e imagen la compania CODISCOS es lo mejor en ell mercado. Dieguito Gale y su sello SALSA-POWER, I'm telling you is the THE BEST en sonido ,imagen y de to'.Este concierto de Tony Vega en Colombia esta bueeeeeeenisimo.
